---
// NewsletterForm.astro — form iscrizione newsletter
---

<div class="newsletter-box">
  <div class="newsletter-icon">✉️</div>
  <h3>Ricevi i miei articoli</h3>
  <p>Ogni volta che pubblico qualcosa di nuovo, te lo mando direttamente.</p>
  <form class="newsletter-form" action="/api/subscribe" method="POST">
    <div class="newsletter-input-row">
      <input
        type="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="la-tua@email.com"
        required
        autocomplete="email"
      />
      <button type="submit">Iscriviti →</button>
    </div>
  </form>
  <p class="newsletter-note">Niente spam. Disiscrizione in un click.</p>
</div>

<style>
.newsletter-box {
  margin: 3rem 0;
  padding: 2rem;
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
  border-radius: 12px;
  text-align: center;
}

.newsletter-icon {
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.newsletter-box h3 {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: var(--text);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.newsletter-box > p {
  color: var(--text-muted);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}

.newsletter-form {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}

.newsletter-input-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 420px;
}

.newsletter-input-row input {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
  background: #1a1a1a;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  color: var(--text);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}

.newsletter-input-row input:focus {
  border-color: var(--accent);
}

.newsletter-input-row input::placeholder {
  color: #555;
}

.newsletter-input-row button {
  padding: 0.65rem 1.25rem;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: #000;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  transition: opacity 0.2s;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.newsletter-input-row button:hover {
  opacity: 0.85;
}

.newsletter-note {
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  color: #555;
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .newsletter-input-row {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
}
</style>
